meico.mpm.elements.styles

Class ArticulationStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • meico.xml.AbstractXmlSubtree
      • meico.mpm.elements.styles.GenericStyle
        • meico.mpm.elements.styles.ArticulationStyle

  • public class ArticulationStyle
extends GenericStyle
    This class interfaces articulation style definitions. Basically, these define an articulation name string (such as "legato", "portato", "agogic accent") and assotiate it with an instance of ArticulationDef.
    Author:
    Axel Berndt
